      <p style="margin-top:2rem" class="dim">The tragedy isn't that people are needy. The tragedy is that their needs are being discipled by systems that profit from keeping them unresolved. The biblical answer isn't to become less dependent. It's to become <strong>rightly dependent</strong> again.</p>
